Fields.annotation:
A single volume from the critical edition of Nietzsche's works. This
                    \textttbook entry explicitly refers to the first volume only. Note the
                    \texttttitle and \textttmaintitle fields. Also note the \textttsorttitle
                    field. We want this entry to be listed after the entry
                    referring to the entire edition
